        "id": "01f0ec779e181a6a8fede0747d8eb443",
        "content": [
          "* If no timeframe is mentioned, ask for one before writing SQL.\r\n",
          "* Queries on bi_output_vg_customer_snapshot require an explicit timeframe.\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "* Do not compare partial current periods (e.g., MTD) to full historical periods unless explicitly requested.\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "* Always create a CTE per table (select required columns only) and join on the requested timeframe and dimensions.\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "* Queries on bi_output_vg_cf_crm_contact must use the \"CF Interactions Only\" filter unless explicitly stated otherwise.\r\n",
          "* CF interaction attribution must use OwnerId (not AccountManagerId).\r\n",
          "* CreatedDate is the source-of-truth contact date.\r\n",
          "* CallDurationInSeconds is the official call duration field.\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "* Customer assignment metrics must use the \"CF Account Managers Only\" filter.\r\n",
          "* For customer assignment questions, count DISTINCT RealCID and define “new assignments” by AssignmentStartAt (with a required timeframe).\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "* last week should be interpreted as the last 7 days\r\n",
          "* Last month should be interpreted as the last 30 days\r\n",
          "* last last year should be interpreted as the last 12 month\r\n"
        ]
      }
